Version 0.4.0
-------------
    * Handle subrepos correctly for go_repo (#191)

Version 0.3.1
-------------
    * Handle some additional cases for third-party packages
    * Some additional flags for debugging

Version 0.3.0
-------------
    * Add search dir option which walks a current directory rather than querying plz.
      Allows running within a Please test.

Version 0.2.3
-------------
    * Allow the caller not to provide any input files at all

Version 0.2.2
-------------
    * Better handle the case of no input files
    * Honour the 'tests' field on input request correctly.

Version 0.2.1
-------------
    * `go_src` dependencies are now explicitly built, ensuring that e.g. code generated from
      protobufs gets downloaded when using remote execution.

Version 0.2.0
-------------
    * `plz build` output now appears on stderr if the terminal is interactive.

Version 0.1.1
-------------
    * Change the release prefix to `plz-gopackagesdriver`.

Version 0.1.0
-------------
    * Initial release of gopackagesdriver tool for Please.
